    "Subsequently, we fine-tune the model on our custom-built dataset for detecting Auslan.",
    "For the training phase, we employ the negative-log-likelihood loss function on the predicted classes for each frame.",
    "During inference, the arg-max of the output vector is utilised to determine the final class.",
    "Gloss correctionThe purpose of gloss correction is to evaluate gloss imitated by Auslan beginners during their self-teaching process.",
    "To ensure efficient inference of real-time application, we pre-extract video embeddings for all glosses using the model trained in Sect. 5.4."
